human-intervention-logs/org.scala-lang:scalap:2.13.13/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-06T13-11-58-330814Z.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/org.scala-lang:scalap:2.13.13/native-test-verify/cycle-0-generateMetadata-2026-05-06T13-13-38-128976Z.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/org.scala-lang:scalap:2.13.13/metadata-fix/codex.log`\n- `stats/org.scala-lang/scalap/2.13.13/stats.json`\n- `stats/org.scala-lang/scalap/2.13.13/execution-metrics.json`\n\nNext steps:\n1. Review the preserved branch and confirm the added resource metadata for `scala/tools/scalap/scalax/rules/scalasig/ByteCode.class`.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=org.scala-lang:scalap:2.13.13` and `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.scala-lang:scalap:2.13.13` from that branch.\n3. If those stay green, continue from the preserved branch for the `library-new-request` PR/update."}}
